# Sovrunn AI Boundaries

AI may generate code, tests, docs, refactors, fixes, and curl demos.

AI must not:

- own architecture decisions
- change resource hierarchy
- change feature sequence
- rename canonical terms
- add future features early
- introduce persistent database storage in Phase 1
- introduce Kubernetes CRDs in Phase 1
- introduce plugin execution in Phase 1
- introduce UI in Phase 1
- introduce AI agent execution in Phase 1
- remove tests or validation to make code pass

When uncertain, stop and ask for human decision.

Use docs/engineering/ai-context-loading-standard.md to decide what context to load. Do not load all docs by default.
